These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
House: modern, futuristic
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the modern house is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| House       | futuristic    | modern    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, april
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Birthday      | april     | december |
| Job           | entrepreneur | lawyer      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
There 2 different types of food: apple, avocado
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the frog is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Pet      | frog | lizard  |
| Food          | apple    | avocado   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, van
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the van is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Transport      | quad-bike       | van |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Music-Genre   | punk           | techno   |

