There 2 different types of food: cucumber, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, german
1. the german is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the german is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Beverage   | 7up         | coffee    |
| Food       | spinach     | cucumber  |
| Hobby      | board-games | chess     |
| Nationality        | german     | nigerian |

