.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, superhero
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, blood-red
1. the coach is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime          | superhero |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Color     | blood-red            | coral       |

 